Author: breadndread
Text: I feel you real hard, my dude. There's a good amount of Chinese/Asian bakeries from my hometown, and the amount of time I spend just grazing and lingering in the store is stupid.   Everything smells so good and tempting, but if I do purchase any, I give it to others to: avoid eating it, get others to experience a bit of culture, and make them like me more :) oh boy love it; using food to validate myself to others, oh boy. It's literally bread and I'm too scared to eat it just fml
